---
title: Ratatouille & Bacon Filo Galette  with Radish Salad
description: Ratatouille - this delicious summery veggie stew just got even better. It has all the same rich flavours, but now it comes packaged in crisp, golden pastry. This is one of those meals where the vegetables really shine - you won’t be missing your staple meat, bacon and three veg when this is on the table!
